data.description: Oak Hampton is a unique cottage community  in Murrells Inlet. Metal roofs, Hardi Plank siding, Paver driveway, natural gas community with tank-less water heater stainless appliances, granite surfaces, 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath on Lake, with pool. This home is a must see. 2 car Garage. Location, Location! Square footage is approximate and not guaranteed. Buyer and buyer's agent are responsible for verification.
